Package org.lfenergy.compas.sct.commons.api

Interface ExtRefEditor

All Known Implementing Classes:
ExtRefService
public interface ExtRefEditor
Service class that will be used to create, update or delete elements related to the TExtRef object.

The following features are supported:

  • ExtRef features
    1. Update the TExtRef reference object for given ExtRefBindingInfo model
    2. Update the TExtRef reference object for given ExtRefSourceInfo model
    3. Update the iedName attribute in all TExtRef
    4. Manage TExtRef Binding For LDevice (inst=LDEPF) within LDEPF configuration
